{"word":"ἀκουάζομαι","slug":"ἀκουάζομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀκουάζομαι</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀκούω'><el>ἀκούω</el></a>\n<br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a>, only in <a href='S:present tense'>pres.</a>\n<p/><i>to hearken</i> or <i>listen to</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>; <el>δαιτὸς ἀκουάζεσθον</el> <i>ye are bidden</i> to the feast, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/>"}]}